main_body:
The aid for dehydrated fodder and sun-dried fodder provided for in Article 3(2) and (3) respectively of Regulation (EC) No 603/95 shall be paid as follows for the 2003/2004 marketing year:
a) the amount of aid for dried fodder shall be reduced to 66,45 EUR per tonne in all the Member States;
b) the aid for sun-dried fodder shall be paid in full.
